ContactUs
=========

Based on http://github.com/bryanmtl/spree_contact_us

Requirements:

1)formtastic

  a) Add you Gemfile-file following line:
    gem 'formtastic', :git => "git://github.com/justinfrench/formtastic.git"
  b) run: bundle install


2) dynamic_form
  
  a) Add you Gemfile-file following line:
     gem 'dynamic_form', :git => 'git://github.com/rails/dynamic_form.git'
  b) run: bundle install

Installation
=======

1. Classic installation:
    a) Add you Gemfile-file
        gem 'contact_us', :require => 'contact_us' :git => 'git://github.com/greendog/spree_contact_us.git'
    b) bundle install
    c) rake contact_us:install
    d) rake db:migrate
    e) rails server

2. Custom installation (not copied migration to main rails-app)
    a) Add you Gemfile-file
        gem 'contact_us', :require => 'contact_us' :git => 'git://github.com/greendog/spree_contact_us.git'
    b) bundle install
    c) rake contact_us:install:assets - copy assets to public dir
    d) rake contact_us:db:migrate   - run only extension migrations
    e) rails server

    Pull requests welcome!